               <div class="container" style="padding-top: 250px;">
                <div class="col-lg-10 col-lg-offset-1 text-center" style="padding: 50px; background-color:rgba(255,255,255,0.80);">
                		<h1 class="main-text-color-gray" style="font-size: 44px; letter-spacing: -1px; padding-bottom: 10px;">Do you love your job? <strong>You should!</strong></h1>
		   <p class="main-text-color2" style="font-size: 26px; padding-bottom: 15px;"><strong>Grow your career with us!</strong> We are looking for people who think big and are ready to roll up their sleeves to make things happen.</p>
                    
                 
