		<div class="row" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">
           
          <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12 col-sm-12" style="padding: 100px;">                	
			<div class="medium" style="font-size: 30px;">R&amp;D jobs at Maplesoft</div><br>
            <p>Join a team of innovators that help companies innovate! Contribute to the advancement of products like Maple, MapleSim and MapleMBSE.</em></p>
            <p>Our R&amp;D team consists of experts in a variety of development and engineering fields, including software development, model-based design, and system-level modeling and analysis. We employ software developers, mathematicians and engineers, at all levels, in a variety of roles. </p>
            <p>Maplesoft&rsquo;s products and services help companies reduce development risk and bring high-quality products to market faster.&nbsp;Through Maple, Maplesoft provides a complete concept-to-deployment environment for advanced analysis and rapid development of technical applications and engineering calculation tools. Maplesoft products and services are used in machine design, manufacturing, robotics, aerospace, and many other fields where engineers face complex challenges. Customers include Boeing, FLSmidth, Ford, Google, NASA, and Samsung. </p>
			<a href="openings.aspx" class="main-text-color medium">View Current Openings</a>
          </div>
			
		<div class="people2 col-lg-6 col-md-12 col-sm-12 center">
		</div>
			
		</div>
     

			  
			  
<div class="row" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">
	
		
						
          <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12 col-sm-12 pull-right" style="padding: 100px;">                	
			<div class="medium" style="font-size: 30px;">Sales &amp; Marketing jobs at Maplesoft</div><br>
              <p>We have progressive and proactive Sales and Marketing teams at Maplesoft. Partnering closely with R&amp;D, our Sales and Marketing people stay up to date on our products and are perfectly positioned to support customers throughout the pre-sales, sales and post-sales process. We hire great people at all levels, from new grads to experienced professionals. </p>
<p>Our talented Marketing team consists of various disciplines including digital marketing, communications and creative design. Marketers work closely with other departments across the company and are able to have a real impact on the company&rsquo;s marketing strategy. </p>
<p>Maplesoft&rsquo;s Customer Success team supports new and existing customers with technical and non-technical issues and uses insights to continually improve our relationships with Maplesoft customers around the world. </p>
<p>Our Sales team includes sales reps and account managers at all levels. We sell our products around the world, directly and through resellers, and have provided mathematics-based software solutions to educators, engineers, and researchers for&nbsp;over 30 years.</p>
			  	<a href="openings.aspx" class="main-text-color medium">View Current Openings</a>
          </div>
	
	<div class="people1 col-lg-6 col-md-12 col-sm-12 center pull-left">
		</div>
	
		</div>

				
	<div class="row" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">
           
          <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12 col-sm-12" style="padding: 100px;">                	
			<div class="medium" style="font-size: 30px;">Students</div><br>
            <p>Maplesoft has an active co-op student and intern program. We welcome students from computer science, engineering, and many other programs each term. Check your schools job site for opportunities to work at Maplesoft. We collaborate with schools around the world on research projects and internships.</p>
