			<div class="container" style="padding-top: 125px;">
    
      <div class="row" style="padding: 0px; margin: 0px;">
          
              	<div class="col-md-7 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 col-lg-4" style="padding-bottom: 30px">
                   <div class="text-center" style="padding-bottom: 15px;">
                       <div class="badge">
                                        <em class="main-text-color fa fa-heart-o"></em>
                                    </div>
					</div>
                       
				 <div class="medium" style="font-size: 22px; padding-bottom: 10px;">Take Care of Yourself</div>
                <ul>
              <li style="padding-bottom: 10px;">Make time for our on-site,<strong> fully equipped fitness facility</strong>. </li>
              <li style="padding-bottom: 10px;">Make use of our comprehensive <strong>group benefits package</strong> for yourself and your family.</li>
              <li style="padding-bottom: 10px;">Enjoy healthy (and some not-as-healthy) <strong>snacks</strong> and <strong>drinks</strong> every day.</li>
                       </ul></div>
          
          
          
          
                        	<div class="col-md-7 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 col-lg-4" style="padding-bottom: 30px">     
                     <div class="text-center" style="padding-bottom: 15px;">
                       <div class="badge pull-center">
                       <em class="main-text-color fa fa-balance-scale"></em></div>
                         <div class="text"></div></div>                    
				 <div class="medium" style="font-size: 22px; padding-bottom: 10px;">Balance</div>
                <ul>
                 <li style="padding-bottom: 10px;"><strong>Work-life balance</strong> is important to us; we know you have lives outside of work!</li>
                  <li style="padding-bottom: 10px;">We value your time and offer <strong>flexible working hours</strong> and minimal interrupts outside of working hours.</li>
                  <li style="padding-bottom: 10px;">Our Time Away From Work program includes <strong>competitive vacation time</strong>, <strong>personal days</strong>, <strong>holiday shut down</strong> and a <strong>Birthday Bonus</strong> (who wants to work on their birthday?!)</li>
                  <!--<li style="padding-bottom: 10px;">Our on-staff <strong>Corporate Concierge</strong> helps you make the most of your spare time by running your errands throughout the day! </li>-->
                       </ul></div>
          
                        	<div class="col-md-7 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 col-lg-4" style="padding-bottom: 30px">   
                    <div class="text-center" style="padding-bottom: 15px;">
                       <div class="badge">
                         <em class="main-text-color fa fa-smile-o"></em>
                                    </div>
                         <div class="text"></div></div>
				 <div class="medium" style="font-size: 22px; padding-bottom: 10px;">Have Some Fun</div>
                <ul>
                  <li style="padding-bottom: 10px;">Take part in <strong>various social events</strong>, <strong>activities</strong> and <strong>celebrations</strong> throughout the year.</li>
                  <li style="padding-bottom: 10px;">From our <strong>Spring Party</strong> and  <strong>golf tournament</strong>, to <strong>regular BBQs</strong> and an annual <strong>pool tournament</strong>, there is something for everyone!</li>
                  <li style="padding-bottom: 10px;">Walk to <strong>St Jacob&rsquo;s market</strong>, nature trails and local restaurants.</li>
                    </ul></div>
</div>
                    <div class="row" style=" margin:0px">
                        
                        <div class="col-md-7 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 col-lg-4" style="padding-bottom: 30px">   
                     <div class="text-center" style="padding-bottom: 15px;">
                       <div class="badge pull-center">
                       <em class="main-text-color fa fa-gift"></em>
                         </div>
                         <div class="text"></div></div>    
			<div class="medium" style="font-size: 22px; padding-bottom: 10px;">Give Back</div>
            <ul>
              <li style="padding-bottom: 10px;">Join our Maplesoft Cares Committee and help us grow our developing <a href="/company/about/social-responsibility-policy.aspx" class="main-text-color medium">Corporate Social Responsibility</a> program with a focus on sustainability, volunteerism and giving.</li>
              <li style="padding-bottom: 10px;">We hold <strong>fundraising activities</strong> throughout the year that allow employees and the company to donate to a charity of your choice.</li>
                    </ul></div>
                     
                         <div class="col-md-7 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 col-lg-4" style="padding-bottom: 30px">   
                    <div class="text-center" style="padding-bottom: 15px;">
                       <div class="badge pull-center">
                       <em class="main-text-color fa fa-info-circle"></em>
                         </div>
                         <div class="text"></div></div>  
                <div class="medium" style="font-size: 22px; padding-bottom: 10px;">Stay Informed</div>
                <ul>
                  <li style="padding-bottom: 10px;">We are <strong>committed</strong> to ensuring all employees have the information they need to do their jobs well.&nbsp;</li>
                  <li style="padding-bottom: 10px;">From regular<strong> one-on-ones</strong> with your leader to quarterly <strong>all-hands meetings</strong>, we share key aspects of how our business is doing and how you are making an impact.</li>
                      </ul></div>
                        
                           <div class="col-md-7 col-sm-12 col-xs-12 col-lg-4" style="padding-bottom: 30px">                       
                    <div class="text-center" style="padding-bottom: 15px;">
                       <div class="badge pull-center">
                       <em class="main-text-color fa fa-lightbulb-o"></em>
                         </div>
                         <div class="text"></div></div>
				<div class="medium" style="font-size: 22px; padding-bottom: 10px;">Be Inspired</div>
                <ul>
                  <li style="padding-bottom: 10px;">At Maplesoft, you will have the opportunity to work with some of the <strong>leading experts</strong> in our field. </li>
                  <li style="padding-bottom: 10px;">We <strong>employ smart people</strong> who are also <strong>genuine</strong> and <strong>passionate</strong>. There is always time for an intellectual conversation or brainstorming session. </li>
                    </ul></div>
                   
     
     

                  
